Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.52,0:00:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(400,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.51,0:00:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Light so glaring that it can't be hidden shatters the silence and revives in this world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.55,0:00:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The violently quaking and thirsty Earth stakes its life and clashes together with sparks
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.31,0:00:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just one more time is enough to create a miracle
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.50,0:00:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For the power to regain the pages of memory lost in the past
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.45,0:00:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fs30}The believing heart that penetrates the darkness searches for the place where its soul sleeps
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.74,0:00:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And burns a sharp glance of eyes that can't sparkle
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.13,0:01:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Two hearts of light and shadow head toward the future that the crystal reflects
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.47,0:01:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now they start to move, these eyes brimming red
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.06,0:01:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Blue-Eyed Kisara"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.16,0:01:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mahado!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.07,0:01:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.66,0:01:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master~!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.79,0:01:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mana...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.25,0:01:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prince!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.38,0:01:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You{\i0} can call the spirits from the stone slabs, can't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.67,0:01:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.05,0:01:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me see my master again!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.13,0:01:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mana...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.22,0:02:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until Mahado is able to heal his wounded soul from the previous battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.56,0:02:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no one will be able to call for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.68,0:02:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, even if we could call Mahado...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.23,0:02:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your {\i1}Heka{\i0} isn't great enough for you to see spirits yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.86,0:02:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Isis...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.44,0:02:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must train harder, Mana.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.61,0:02:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you can inherit Mahado's will!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.91,0:02:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.62,0:02:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear to become a great magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.70,0:02:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.00,0:02:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}swear!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.63,0:02:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Other Me's...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.63,0:02:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Memory World!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.64,0:02:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you've finally found it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.35,0:02:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The True Door.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.14,0:02:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is as far as I can guide you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.44,0:02:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beyond this point lies a vigorous world where only the Pharaoh
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.61,0:02:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,can recall its memories\N from within his heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.65,0:02:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, he who has been chosen by the Millennium Puzzle!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.82,0:03:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be courageous and go on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.70,0:03:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.91,0:03:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But by "go on", you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.28,0:03:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do we?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.62,0:03:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.41,0:03:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.71,0:03:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.37,0:03:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.46,0:03:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The most important thing is whether or not Mahado killed Bakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.09,0:03:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he got away, there's a good chance he's stolen the Millennium Ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.85,0:03:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, if we wish to confirm the truth of this matter, based on the scale of that cave-in,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.89,0:03:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it could take several weeks to remove all the rubble.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.19,0:03:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Bakura takes hold of the Millennium Ring during that time frame...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.07,0:03:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Isis... Can you see Bakura's future with the Millennium Tauk?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.57,0:03:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... I can see nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.83,0:03:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all because of\N Mahado's incompetence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.91,0:03:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isis, I am most certain you saw Mahado's actions in the future before this happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.38,0:03:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am terribly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.38,0:04:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that you cannot see Bakura's future is rather questionable...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.09,0:04:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll send my {\i1}Ka{\i0}, Spiria, to the valley and use her Clear Voyance
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.93,0:04:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to search while I stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.93,0:04:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I leave it to you, Isis!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.19,0:04:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great Pharaoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.60,0:04:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This has become quite an urgent matter after what we have experienced.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.98,0:04:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As such, I would like to take my troops so we can scour the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.82,0:04:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.11,0:04:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we let this continue, we will continue to let our tears of sadness flow into the Nile!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.24,0:04:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must {\i1}act!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.16,0:04:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please allow me to head a search for Bakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.62,0:04:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly, since we do not know if Bakura is alive or dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.00,0:04:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a search would be for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.63,0:04:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.63,0:04:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But whatever you do, you {\i1}must not{\i0} threaten the people!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.38,0:04:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.60,0:04:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.64,0:04:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We really went to Ancient Egypt!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.02,0:04:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.90,0:04:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, don't you think we stand out in these get-ups?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.69,0:05:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're probably right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.44,0:05:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But no one seems to have taken notice of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.90,0:05:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.66,0:05:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure they're all staring at us like we're suspicious or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.87,0:05:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or not...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.95,0:05:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.20,0:05:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.04,0:05:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't think we look suspicious or anything, do yo-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.21,0:05:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.17,0:05:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She walked right through me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.63,0:05:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Millennium Puzzle's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.34,0:05:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. This is my other self's\N Memory World.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.02,0:05:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this world, no one knows who we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.14,0:05:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, to the people of this world, we don't even exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.90,0:05:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that means even the other Yugi can't see us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.94,0:05:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not really sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.40,0:05:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But as long as we still remember him...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.41,0:05:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he still...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.12,0:06:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto, do you truly believe that Bakura is still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.67,0:06:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a foolish question.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.09,0:06:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His {\i1}Ka{\i0} had enough power within it to fight against a God on equal ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.68,0:06:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you not witness that yourself back there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.48,0:06:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mahado died in vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.19,0:06:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The situation has gotten even worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.60,0:06:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean the Millennium Ring was...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.19,0:06:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.94,0:06:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he puts on the Millennium Ring, I have no doubt that his evil will grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.61,0:06:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we do not reinforce our alignment of {\i1}Ka{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.41,0:06:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he will eventually become something we cannot handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.41,0:06:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shada...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.33,0:06:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Millennium Ankh has the power to search people's souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.37,0:06:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Among the commoners, there must be some who have powerful {\i1}Ka{\i0} within their souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.88,0:06:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.04,0:06:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we are Holy Priests, we are not permitted
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.30,0:06:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to look into the souls of the innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.05,0:06:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then tell me this...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.09,0:06:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we were to fight Bakura again now that he holds the Millennium Ring in our present state,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.39,0:06:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,do you believe we could oppose him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.10,0:06:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or do you instead intend to put the Pharaoh in danger once again
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.39,0:07:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by relying on the power of the Gods?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.44,0:07:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.07,0:07:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shada, Mahado's actions were foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.57,0:07:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, we cannot allow the will he had to fight against Bakura's God-like powers
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.49,0:07:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by himself go to waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.29,0:07:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Search anyone and everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.66,0:07:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those dressed suspiciously, those unprecedented, insubordination...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.37,0:07:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to round up anyone who seems questionable, regardless of their age...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.59,0:07:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and bring them here on the double!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.89,0:07:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...increasing...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.09,0:07:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's increasing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.80,0:07:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, the fear and despair will continue to increase!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.23,0:07:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Lord Priest!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.69,0:07:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what crime am I being suspected of?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.74,0:07:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have yet to commit any sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.91,0:07:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the chances of you doing so eventually are very high.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.83,0:08:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.20,0:08:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lemme go, goddamn you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.25,0:08:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Seto, we have captured an escaped criminal in the local bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.09,0:08:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you\N actually found a criminal...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.38,0:08:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shada, search this man's {\i1}Ka.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.43,0:08:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Millennium Ankh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.76,0:08:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me this man's soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.48,0:08:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An evil {\i1}Ka{\i0} has been created within this man's wicked mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.27,0:08:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not at a very high {\i1}Heka{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.28,0:08:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if we leave it be, it could cause trouble again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.15,0:08:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's trash then...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.32,0:08:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if there's any chance for it to grow stronger...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.78,0:08:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lock him up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.91,0:08:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.79,0:08:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pl-Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.33,0:08:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just made it out of the desert alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.42,0:08:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear I haven't committed any crimes after doing so!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.79,0:08:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The very fact we confirmed an evil {\i1}Ka{\i0} resides within you,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.88,0:08:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,more or less confirms that you've committed crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.05,0:08:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's freakin' outrageous!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.93,0:08:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If y'all do this to me,\N you're gonna be cursed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.80,0:09:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I seen it wit' my own eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.56,0:09:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I seen a God flyin' 'round right smack in the middle of the desert!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.68,0:09:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was thanks to it that I was able to survive and make it back to the city!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.10,0:09:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.31,0:09:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was guided here by the White Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.32,0:09:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Did you just say the White Dragon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.12,0:09:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't mistaken, no sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.53,0:09:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The White Dragon is in this city!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.70,0:09:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know for a fact that it's 'round here watchin' over me this very minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.29,0:09:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The White Dragon's... in this city?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.00,0:09:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.63,0:09:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.63,0:09:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.75,0:09:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really gonna be punished for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.80,0:09:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna be punished by the White Dragon!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.40,0:09:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.23,0:09:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! H-Hold it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.07,0:09:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.03,0:09:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, what's wrong with you, Jounouchi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.66,0:10:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so hungry I can't even move!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.74,0:10:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! We're like {\i1}ghosts{\i0}\N right now, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.91,0:10:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You {\i1}can't{\i0} be hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.16,0:10:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you put it like {\i1}that{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starving, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.92,0:10:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda! Not {\i1}you{\i0}, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.22,0:10:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we can't touch anything here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.47,0:10:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that means we can't {\i1}eat{\i0} anything either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.14,0:10:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.81,0:10:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.86,0:10:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ain't that guy pretty weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.94,0:10:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How so?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.82,0:10:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's sitting there stuffing his face like a pig,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.82,0:10:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but no one even notices.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.32,0:10:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.95,0:10:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.49,0:10:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hey!\N - Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.49,0:10:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Let us eat those~!\N - Let us eat those~!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.08,0:10:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.12,0:10:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you really {\i1}can{\i0} see us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.75,0:10:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.21,0:10:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Why, you...!\N -Why, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.09,0:11:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Damn you!\N - Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.27,0:11:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.02,0:11:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- C'mon!\N - C'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.02,0:11:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- The heck?\N - The heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.36,0:11:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just get out of this city!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.86,0:11:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got no doubt this woman's a witch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.32,0:11:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.99,0:11:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you jerks! Whad'daya mean, ganging up on her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.54,0:11:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't stand guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.33,0:11:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- ...who pick on the weak!\N - ...who pick on the weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.13,0:11:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.05,0:11:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, I forgot these guys can't see us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.34,0:11:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The stones are going right through us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.59,0:11:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Ain't there anything we can do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.22,0:11:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's gong on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.97,0:11:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta be {\i1}kidding!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.14,0:11:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.31,0:11:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.50,0:12:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Seto?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.33,0:12:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is this...!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.00,0:12:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This woman's {\i1}Heka{\i0}... is far too much for the Ankh to measure!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.09,0:12:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an {\i1}enormous{\i0} {\i1}Heka{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.30,0:12:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shada!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.80,0:12:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I never would have imagined she would be holding so much {\i1}Heka{\i0}...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.39,0:12:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.10,0:12:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's an enormous...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.31,0:12:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...{\i1}Heka{\i0} inside of this woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.52,0:12:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this woman into custody immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.40,0:12:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give her sufficient water and food!\N Then nurse her back to good health!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.82,0:12:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.02,0:12:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scurry along, vicious beasts!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.78,0:12:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, I will arrest every single one of you remaining here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.53,0:12:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice one, Dude-Who-Looks-Like-Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.28,0:12:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.54,0:12:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm-hmm!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.62,0:12:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those two are holding the Millennium Rod and the Millennium Ankh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.04,0:12:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That must mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.79,0:13:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That man is the same priest carved onto the Stone Slab of Memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.55,0:13:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one is to speak of this to the Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.22,0:13:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have the luxury to be {\i1}merciful{\i0} and {\i1}lenient{\i0} as in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.80,0:13:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shada, let's return to the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.31,0:13:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...! He just said "palace"!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.31,0:13:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So if we follow those two...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.77,0:13:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should be able to see the other me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.27,0:13:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Then let's get going to the palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.57,0:13:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mhm!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.70,0:13:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.87,0:13:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place is {\i1}too much!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.54,0:13:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on and hurry up, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.58,0:13:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, the doors are...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.67,0:13:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hell're we gonna do now?!\N They closed the doors!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.26,0:13:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get your undies in a twist!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.67,0:13:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause we're {\i1}ghosts{\i0} here, you see!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.26,0:13:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A measly little {\i1}door{\i0} ain't stoppin' nobo-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.81,0:13:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.77,0:13:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the hell's going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.27,0:13:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I smashed right into the thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.31,0:13:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.27,0:14:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that means we can't enter the palace?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.82,0:14:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bobasa and friends can't go in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.40,0:14:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- It's {\i1}you!{\i0}\N - It's {\i1}you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.32,0:14:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Bobasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.87,0:14:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was a {\i1}wee bit{\i0} surprised back there,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.70,0:14:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but now I see you people aren't bad guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.95,0:14:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bobasa saw you guys trying to help that woman that collapsed back there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.08,0:14:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys're good people!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.54,0:14:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.88,0:14:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- The hell?!\N - The hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.05,0:14:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'ma giving you these!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.05,0:14:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- FOOD~!\N - FOOD~!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.47,0:14:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, why can you touch things in this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.98,0:14:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because... Uhhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.69,0:14:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bobasa don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.40,0:14:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- He ate it!\N - He ate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.74,0:14:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, how do we enter the palace?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.78,0:14:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bobasa's got no idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.75,0:14:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- He ate it again!\N - He ate it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.58,0:15:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, how-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.96,0:15:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Don't ask him anything, Anzu!\N - Don't ask him anything, Anzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.54,0:15:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bobasa gets really hungry whenever he has to think!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.01,0:15:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- S-See?!\N - S-See?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.38,0:15:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- So don't ask him anything right now!\N - So don't ask him anything right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.38,0:15:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what do you propose we do about this then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.47,0:15:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bobasa hasn't a clue!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.85,0:15:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- He's gonna eat them!\N - He's gonna eat them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.40,0:15:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Other Me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.44,0:15:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to see you right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.70,0:15:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A voice called out to me just now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.21,0:15:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it midnight yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.50,0:15:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, the moonlight has spread far.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.96,0:15:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If something happens,\N we'll notice immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.92,0:15:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.17,0:15:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time I attack at {\i1}night.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.93,0:15:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like a thief {\i1}should.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.18,0:15:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In our Ultimate Dark Game,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.89,0:15:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,something big that happened 3,000 years ago is about to happen in a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.06,0:16:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's already called out one of the three God Cards
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.64,0:16:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that were not able\N to be summoned prior.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.77,0:16:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to have him call out the others right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.23,0:16:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I have one more \Nthing I must prepare...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.45,0:16:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After getting the Millennium Ring and furthering the evolution of Diabound...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.16,0:16:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...I can now erase my very presence right under your noses!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.37,0:16:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Akhenaden!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.58,0:16:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.88,0:16:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bring you my report.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.84,0:16:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The {\i1}Ka{\i0} hunt in the city went much better than expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.72,0:16:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, there were many people in the city hiding superior {\i1}Ka{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.10,0:16:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me, Seto...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.02,0:16:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean you {\i1}arrested{\i0} those people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.39,0:16:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean to say I shouldn't have?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.81,0:16:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto... It's not too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.61,0:16:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let those innocent people go free!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.65,0:16:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sin creates fear in one's heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.11,0:16:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fear leads one to endless darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.95,0:16:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Akhenaden.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.95,0:17:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you compare us to the commoners...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.29,0:17:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you propose is the difference between us?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.46,0:17:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Faced with the fall of the dynasty, we, too, are faced with immeasurable fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.79,0:17:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All that I do is for Pharaoh and our great country of Egypt!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.51,0:17:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not believe I have done anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.84,0:17:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.84,0:17:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still have work left to complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.35,0:17:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.10,0:17:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Seto...! You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.57,0:17:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...trying to walk down the same mistaken path I once did?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.29,0:17:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You are...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.75,0:17:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.54,0:17:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the woman's condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.92,0:17:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir! She is still asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.42,0:17:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.38,0:18:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The White God with blue eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.10,0:18:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, that's not all it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.39,0:18:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The being that lies within her heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.35,0:18:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know this woman...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.53,0:18:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We picked up somethin' nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.12,0:18:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's pretty rare for this country!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.41,0:18:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Havin' white hair and blue eyes like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.67,0:18:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We'll follow ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.38,0:18:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.51,0:18:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sssh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.88,0:18:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll let you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.84,0:18:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.26,0:18:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You little-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.64,0:18:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.52,0:18:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They got away!\N The girl ran away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.36,0:18:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are they following us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.32,0:18:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.19,0:18:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Good. I'll give you this horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.86,0:18:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go on alone from here on out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.45,0:19:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you keep straight on this path, you'll reach the nearest town shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.78,0:19:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then you'll have to do\N what you can to escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.58,0:19:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.29,0:19:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is your name?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.54,0:19:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Seto!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.12,0:19:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thank you, Seto!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.00,0:19:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thank you!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.14,0:19:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.05,0:19:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...my village!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.23,0:19:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn them...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.35,0:19:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.15,0:19:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mother!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.86,0:19:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Keep looking!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.61,0:19:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.98,0:19:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where's that blue-eyed brat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.03,0:19:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I-I don't know...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.95,0:19:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.82,0:19:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mother!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.20,0:19:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're the kid from before!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.58,0:19:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where'd that girl go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.33,0:19:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.92,0:19:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.42,0:19:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.50,0:19:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let {\i0}go{\i1} of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.09,0:20:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.89,0:20:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.39,0:20:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.23,0:20:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wh-What the hell's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.85,0:20:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.61,0:20:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.75,0:20:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.91,0:20:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is the same girl from that time...\N And I've seen the White Dragon myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.22,0:20:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, geezer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.43,0:20:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're {\i1}that slow{\i0}, the match'll be over before you even summon our your {\i1}Ka{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.28,0:21:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.53,0:21:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ripping the Millennium Eye right from you would be a simple task, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.83,0:21:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I have a little {\i1}job{\i0}\N I'd like you to do for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.33,0:21:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like you did 3,000 years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.34,0:21:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know {\i1}all about it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.26,0:21:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you did to the Kul Elna village in order to create the Millennium Items.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.51,0:21:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that you abandoned your only son, Seto, in order to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.73,0:21:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To show us now...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.03,0:22:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...a map isn't needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.50,0:22:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Only what tore apart the darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.63,0:22:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...the hope that lies in my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.76,0:22:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Without deciding on a goal...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.19,0:22:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll just take a step toward my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.82,0:22:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}EYE'S, while I feel them...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.28,0:22:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll find your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.92,0:22:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh! EYE'S, if what I wished for...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.13,0:23:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...shudders my very soul...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.74,0:23:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...a Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.75,0:23:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We managed to get into the other Yugi's Lost Memory World,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.21,0:23:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but to the people of this world, we don't even exist!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.09,0:23:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't even enter the royal palace, so what'll we do now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.76,0:23:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the same time, there's Akhenaden who was attacked by Bakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.56,0:23:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the horrible memory of the creation of the Millennium Items?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.19,0:23:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.85,0:23:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Secret Behind the Birth of the Millennium Items"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.98,0:23:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please look forward to it!
